{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was taken to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you can still see the marks of the stitches that I had from there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And another time, we were always diving kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were messing around on the diving board, the 10-meter board.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one day, I was pushed off it onto the stones below kind of thing, not into the water, but onto the tiles kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I had various injuries then and went to the hospital again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But yeah, those are things I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But in Naarden there was even more of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And perhaps I was older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "By that time, I was 13, 14-- no, 13, something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So maybe I have a better memory of it by then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So, as I say, the ice skating and football, I remember very well-- cycling, of course, always.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little about life at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father obviously still worked at this bank at that time in, in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he traveled to Amsterdam every day and worked there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't believe that my mother ever really worked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, we had Eve, who was quite young, six, something like that, five, four.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I think mother spent most of the time at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, wives didn't go out to work too much, in those days, anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I can't remember really much about home life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- well, I can't even remember ever listening to the radio, for example.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously, there was no television or things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and I can't remember much about newspapers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The other thing-- I remember that we must have read newspapers-- is that I was very interested in cycling and the Tour de France, for example.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
